65
00:04:00,992 --> 00:04:03,369
<i>What in the world are
you planning, Light Yagami?</i>

66
00:04:04,036 --> 00:04:06,247
<i>When you take hold of
the notebook once more,</i>

67
00:04:06,748 --> 00:04:12,170
<i>all your memories of when you had
the Death Note will return.</i>

68
00:04:13,254 --> 00:04:14,380
<i>But...</i>

69
00:04:16,007 --> 00:04:17,383
Ryuzaki, this is it.

70
00:04:26,768 --> 00:04:28,895
It's a Shinigami...isn't it?

71
00:04:29,896 --> 00:04:33,232
