75
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:42,408
<i>The Second Mra. ..</i> !

76
00:04:42,742 --> 00:04:43,826
<i>Two books!</i>

77
00:04:44,911 --> 00:04:47,205
<i>There are more than
two notebooks in existence!</i>

78
00:04:48,122 --> 00:04:49,415
<i>This isn't finished yet...</i>

79
00:05:00,134 --> 00:05:02,011
<i>A Shinigami?</i>

80
00:05:03,554 --> 00:05:04,972
<i>Write the name in the Death Note.</i>

81
00:05:06,182 --> 00:05:07,350
<i>...and L.</i>

82
00:05:10,269 --> 00:05:11,437
<i>lam L.</i>

83
00:05:19,237 --> 00:05:21,155
