that notebook belongs to Ryuk.

100
00:06:18,713 --> 00:06:22,842
Ryuk, drop that notebook on the ground
of the Human World again.

101
00:06:23,634 --> 00:06:25,887
Huh? Well, okay.

102
00:06:30,433 --> 00:06:32,101
Now ownership of
this notebook belongs to me again.

103
00:06:32,977 --> 00:06:36,522
Hold on, it's just gone around.
Nothing's changed.

104
00:06:37,315 --> 00:06:38,816
Yeah, that may be true.

105
00:06:39,483 --> 00:06:42,236
<i>But there will come a time
when this will be useful.</i>

106
00:06:43,446 --> 00:06:45,364
This notebook,
the one I first received...

107
00:06:46,741 --> 00:06:48,534
I'm now going to return it
to you, Ryuk.

108
00:06:48,910 --> 00:06:49,952
Give it back to Rem.

109
00:06:53,789 --> 00:06:54,874
Here.

110
00:07:01,047 --> 00:07:02,840
Rem, give that to a person

111
00:07:02,924 --> 00:07:05,384
