the name Hideki Ryuga?</i>

262
00:17:00,437 --> 00:17:03,941
<i>I want you to write his name
in the notebook. . .and kill him.</i>

263
00:17:04,650 --> 00:17:06,527
<i>Also, burn this letter,</i>

264
00:17:06,735 --> 00:17:11,281
<i>hide a few pages of the notebook
with you, and bury the notebook.</i>

265
00:17:12,282 --> 00:17:14,034
<i>When you meet me again,</i>

266
00:17:14,451 --> 00:17:16,954
