a piece of the notebook.</i>

267
00:17:17,621 --> 00:17:20,457
<i>If you do this, Misa Amane, I will...</i>

268
00:17:21,333 --> 00:17:23,210
<i>- love you for the rest of my life.
- "love you for the rest of my life. "</i>

